source: TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_SEQ_00<tab>Laxio of Little Solace remains unconvinced of your intentions.
target: TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_SEQ_00<tab>Laxio n'est pas encore ami avec vous...

source: TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_SEQ_01<tab>Laxio demands that you obey his every command as proof that you are a friend to the sylphs. First, /poke his back to scratch an itch.
target: TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_SEQ_01<tab>Pour faire plaisir à Laxio, <var 1A 02 /var>touchez-le<var 1A 01 /var> légèrement du doigt.

source: TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_SEQ_02<tab>By touching Laxio, you have been afflicted with a sylphic curse that turns one's skin to moss. /examineself and ascertain its dire effect.
target: TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_SEQ_02<tab>Laxio vous a jeté un sort<var 1D /var>! <var 1A 02 /var>Regardez-vous<var 1A 01 /var> pour voir à quoi vous ressemblez maintenant.

source: TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_SEQ_03<tab>The curse was a lie; Laxio was only fooling you. Express your adulation and /congratulate him on his brilliant ruse.
TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_SEQ_04<tab>Your sense of humor pleases Laxio, who now welcomes you to Little Solace with wings outspread.
target: TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_SEQ_04<tab>Laxio semble ravi de votre petit entretien. Vous avez un ami de plus.

source: TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_LAXIO_000_000<tab>Walking one may dance many dances, but this one still doesn't like walking ones! Why? Because walking ones don't listen! That's why!
target:
TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_LAXIO_000_000<tab>C'est vous qui dansez un peu partout, dont j'ai entendu parler<var 1D /var>?
Vous dansez bien, mais ça ne suffit pas à me toucher<var 1D /var>!
Vous essayez de vous faire des amis, j'ai cru deviner<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_LAXIO_000_001<tab>If walking one wants to be friend to this one, walking one should listen, and listen good! This one has itchy spot on back. Walking one should <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>poke<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> it.
target:
TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_LAXIO_000_001<tab>Faites tout ce que je vous dis, si vous voulez qu'on le soit<var 1D /var>!
D'abord, mon dos me gratte, alors si vous pouviez le <var 1A 02 /var>toucher<var 1A 01 /var> du doigt...

source: TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_LAXIO_000_010<tab>This one has itchy spot on back. Walking one should <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>poke<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> it. And not too hard! This one has sensitive fibers.
TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_LAXIO_000_015<tab>Tee hee! Walking one fell into trap! Touching this one turns walking ones' skin into moss!
target:
TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_LAXIO_000_015<tab>Bien joué<var 1D /var>! Pour la peine, je vais vous transformer<var 1D /var>!
Vous allez devenir tout<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> vert<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> comme un fourré<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_LAXIO_000_016<tab>Tee hee! Mossy one's skin turns greener and greener! Mossy one should <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>examine self<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> to see how silly mossy one has become!
target:
TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_LAXIO_000_016<tab>Maintenant, <var 1A 02 /var>regardez-vous<var 1A 01 /var><var 1D /var>!
Admirez comme vous avez l'air foufou<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_LAXIO_000_020<tab>Do walking one's ears not hear? This one said walking one should <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>poke<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> this one's back!
TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_LAXIO_000_030<tab>Tee hee! Mossy one's skin turns greener and greener! Mossy one should <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>examine self<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>!
target:
TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_LAXIO_000_030<tab>Mon sort a vraiment bien marché<var 1D /var>!
Admirez le résultat avec <var 1A 02 /var>se regarder<var 1A 01 /var><var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_LAXIO_000_035<tab>Hee hee hee! Walking one is so silly! There is no curse, silly one!
target:
TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_LAXIO_000_035<tab>Hi hi hi, c'était une blague, je rigolais<var 1D /var>!
En fait, je ne vous ai rien fait<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_LAXIO_000_036<tab>This one tricked silly one good, yes? This one is smart. Silly one should <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>congratulate<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> this one for being so very smart.
target:
TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_LAXIO_000_036<tab>Je vous ai bien eu<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>, j'ai bien ri<var 1D /var>!
Vous devriez me <var 1A 02 /var>féliciter<var 1A 01 /var> pour ma drôlerie<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_LAXIO_000_040<tab>Does walking one's brain turn to moss, too? This one said mossy one should <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>examine self<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>. What is mossy one waiting for?
TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_LAXIO_000_050<tab>This one is smart. Silly one should <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>congratulate<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> this one for being so very smart.
target:
TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_LAXIO_000_050<tab>Im<var 16 /var>pres<var 16 /var>sionnant, pas vrai<var 1D /var>?
<var 1A 02 /var>Félicitez-moi<var 1A 01 /var> pour ce bon tour que j'ai fait<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_LAXIO_000_055<tab>That's right, silly one! This one is very, very smart one. Silly one is smart to know this.
target:
TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_LAXIO_000_055<tab>Bien, bien<var 1D /var>! J'ai vraiment un sens de l'humour unique<var 1D /var>!
On ne dirait pas, avec mon air angélique<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_LAXIO_000_056<tab>Silly one makes this one laugh. This one likes to laugh. Maybe silly one is not so bad, after all.
target:
TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_LAXIO_000_056<tab>Grâce à vous, j'ai bien ri<var 1D /var>!
À partir d'aujourd'hui, nous serons amis<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_GAIUSA106_00720_LAXIO_000_060<tab>Silly one is no fun! This one tricked silly one. Silly one should <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>congratulate<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> this one for being so very smart.
